/* å•†å“è©³ç´°ã‚¨ãƒªã‚¢ï¼ˆDOMæ“ä½œã®ãƒ¡ã‚¤ãƒ³å¯¾è±¡ï¼‰ */
.product-details {
    background: #f8f9fa;
    border-radius: 15px;
    padding: 15px;
    margin-top: 15px;
    display: none;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    text-align: left;
}

.product-details.show {
    display: block;
    opacity: 1;
    animation: slideIn 0.3s ease;
}

@keyframes slideIn {
    from { transform: translateY(-10px); opacity: 0; }
    to { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
}

.product-details h3 {
    color: #333;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    font-size: 16px;
}

.product-details p {
    color: #666;
